## Day-Wise Project Plan

### Day 1 – Project Planning
- Selected project title  
- Defined objectives and problem statement  
- Studied basics of speech-to-text systems  

### Day 2 – Technology Selection
- Selected programming language (Python)  
- Identified deep learning model for speech recognition  
- Installed required libraries and tools  

### Day 3 – Audio Input Handling
- Implemented microphone/audio file input  
- Preprocessed audio data  
- Tested audio capture functionality  

### Day 4 – Speech Recognition Implementation
- Integrated deep learning speech recognition model  
- Converted speech input to text  
- Tested with sample audio files  

### Day 5 – Accuracy Improvement
- Improved recognition accuracy  
- Handled noise and speech variations  
- Optimized model performance  

### Day 6 – Testing and Validation
- Tested system with different users  
- Verified output correctness  
- Fixed errors and bugs  

### Day 7 – Documentation and Submission
- Prepared README and project documentation  
- Uploaded project to GitHub  
- Final testing and project submission  

